{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I hope you'll understand my English."},{"time":3000,"text":"In the mornings it is terrible, and the afternoon is worst."},{"time":9000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":12000,"text":"During many years, I made some speeches starting with this"},{"time":17000,"text":"saying: \"City is not a problem, it's a solution.\""},{"time":22000,"text":"And more and more, I'm convinced that"},{"time":28000,"text":"it's not only a solution for a country,"},{"time":32000,"text":"but it's a solution for the problem of climate change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37000,"text":"But we have a very pessimistic approach about the cities."},{"time":44000,"text":"I'm working in cities for almost 40 years,"},{"time":48000,"text":"and where every mayor is trying to tell me his city is so big,"},{"time":55000,"text":"or the other mayors say, \"We don't have financial resources,\""},{"time":61000,"text":"I would like to say"},{"time":64000,"text":"from the experience I had: every city in the world"},{"time":68000,"text":"can be improved in less than three years."},{"time":76000,"text":"There's no matter of scale. It's not a question of scale,"},{"time":80000,"text":"it's not a question of financial resources."},{"time":83000,"text":"Every problem in a city has to have its own equation of co-responsibility"},{"time":90000,"text":"and also a design."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93000,"text":"So to start, I want to introduce some characters"},{"time":99000,"text":"from a book I made for teenagers."},{"time":102000,"text":"The best example of quality of life is the turtle"},{"time":108000,"text":"because the turtle is an example of living and working together."},{"time":115000,"text":"And when you realize that the casque of the turtle"},{"time":120000,"text":"looks like an urban tessitura,"},{"time":125000,"text":"and can we imagine, if we cut the casque of the turtle, how sad she's going to be?"},{"time":134000,"text":"And that's what we're doing in our cities:"},{"time":136000,"text":"living here, working here, having leisure here."},{"time":139000,"text":"And most of the people are leaving the city"},{"time":143000,"text":"and living outside of the city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146000,"text":"So, the other character is Otto, the automobile."},{"time":152000,"text":"He is invited for a party -- he never wants to leave."},{"time":157000,"text":"The chairs are on the tables and still drinking,"},{"time":162000,"text":"and he drinks a lot. (Laughter)"},{"time":164000,"text":"And he coughs a lot. Very egotistical:"},{"time":168000,"text":"he carries only one or two people"},{"time":171000,"text":"and he asks always for more infrastructure."},{"time":178000,"text":"Freeways."},{"time":180000,"text":"He's a very demanding person."},{"time":183000,"text":"And on the other hand, Accordion, the friendly bus,"},{"time":187000,"text":"he carries 300 people --"},{"time":190000,"text":"275 in Sweden; 300 Brazilians. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":201000,"text":"Speaking about the design: every city has its own design."},{"time":206000,"text":"Curitiba, my city: three million in the metropolitan area,"},{"time":210000,"text":"1,800,000 people in the city itself."},{"time":215000,"text":"Curitiba, Rio: it's like two birds kissing themselves."},{"time":218000,"text":"Oaxaca, San Francisco -- it's very easy:"},{"time":221000,"text":"Market Street, Van Ness and the waterfront."},{"time":224000,"text":"And every city has its own design."},{"time":228000,"text":"But to make it happen, sometimes you have to propose a scenario"},{"time":232000,"text":"and to propose a design --"},{"time":235000,"text":"an idea that everyone, or the large majority,"},{"time":238000,"text":"will help you to make it happen."},{"time":241000,"text":"And that's the structure of the city of Curitiba."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"And it's an example of living and working together."},{"time":251000,"text":"And this is where we have more density;"},{"time":256000,"text":"it's where we have more public transport."},{"time":259000,"text":"So, this system started in '74. We started with 25,000 passengers a day,"},{"time":267000,"text":"now it's 2,200,000 passengers a day."},{"time":270000,"text":"And it took 25 years until another city ..."},{"time":274000,"text":"which is Bogota, and they did a very good job."},{"time":279000,"text":"And now there's 83 cities all over the world that they"},{"time":284000,"text":"are doing what they call the BRT of Curitiba."},{"time":288000,"text":"And one thing: it's important not for only your own city;"},{"time":295000,"text":"every city, besides its normal problems,"},{"time":299000,"text":"they have a very important role"},{"time":302000,"text":"in being with the whole humanity."},{"time":305000,"text":"That means mostly two main issues --"},{"time":310000,"text":"mobility and sustainability -- are becoming very important for the cities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315000,"text":"And this is an articulated bus, double-articulated."},{"time":320000,"text":"And we are very close to my house."},{"time":323000,"text":"You can come when you are in Curitiba and have a coffee there."},{"time":328000,"text":"And that's the evolution of the system."},{"time":330000,"text":"What in the design that made the difference"},{"time":334000,"text":"is the boarding tubes:"},{"time":336000,"text":"the boarding tube gives to the bus the same performance as a subway."},{"time":341000,"text":"That's why, I'm trying to say,"},{"time":346000,"text":"it's like metro-nizing the bus."},{"time":348000,"text":"This is the design of the bus,"},{"time":354000,"text":"and you can pay before entering the bus you're boarding."},{"time":357000,"text":"And for handicapped, they can use this as a normal system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365000,"text":"What I'm trying to say is"},{"time":368000,"text":"the major contribution on carbon emissions are from the cars --"},{"time":374000,"text":"more than 50 percent -- so when we depend only on cars, it's ..."},{"time":383000,"text":"-- that's why when we're talking about sustainability,"},{"time":387000,"text":"it's not enough, green buildings."},{"time":390000,"text":"It's not enough, a new materials."},{"time":393000,"text":"It's not enough, new sources of energy."},{"time":396000,"text":"It's the concept of the city, the design of the city,"},{"time":400000,"text":"that's also important, too. And also, how to teach the children."},{"time":411000,"text":"I'll speak on this later on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":416000,"text":"Our idea of mobility is trying"},{"time":419000,"text":"to make the connections between all the systems."},{"time":422000,"text":"We started in '83, proposing for the city of Rio"},{"time":427000,"text":"how to connect the subway with the bus."},{"time":430000,"text":"The subway was against, of course."},{"time":433000,"text":"And 23 years after, they called us to develop -- we're developing this idea."},{"time":439000,"text":"And you can understand how different it's going to be,"},{"time":443000,"text":"the image of Rio with the system --"},{"time":446000,"text":"one-minute frequency."},{"time":450000,"text":"And it's not Shanghai,"},{"time":452000,"text":"it's not being colored during the day, only at night"},{"time":456000,"text":"it will look this way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":459000,"text":"And before you say it's a Norman Foster design,"},{"time":464000,"text":"we designed this in '83."},{"time":469000,"text":"And this is the model,"},{"time":470000,"text":"how it's going to work. So, it's the same system;"},{"time":475000,"text":"the vehicle is different. And that's the model."},{"time":482000,"text":"What I'm trying to say is, I'm not trying"},{"time":485000,"text":"to prove which system of transport is better."},{"time":491000,"text":"I'm trying to say we have to combine"},{"time":494000,"text":"all the systems, and with one condition:"},{"time":499000,"text":"never -- if you have a subway, if you have surface systems,"},{"time":505000,"text":"if you have any kind of system --"},{"time":508000,"text":"never compete in the same space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":513000,"text":"And coming back to the car, I always used to say"},{"time":520000,"text":"that the car is like your mother-in-law:"},{"time":525000,"text":"you have to have good relationship with her,"},{"time":528000,"text":"but she cannot command your life."},{"time":533000,"text":"So, when the only woman in your life is your mother-in-law,"},{"time":543000,"text":"you have a problem. (Laughter)"},{"time":547000,"text":"So, all the ideas about how to transform through design --"},{"time":554000,"text":"old quarries and open universities and botanic garden --"},{"time":561000,"text":"all of it's related to how we teach the children."},{"time":569000,"text":"And the children, we teach during six months how to separate their garbage."},{"time":573000,"text":"And after, the children teach their parents."},{"time":578000,"text":"And now we have 70 percent --"},{"time":581000,"text":"since 20 years, it's the highest rate of separation of garbage in the world."},{"time":587000,"text":"Seven zero."},{"time":589000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":594000,"text":"So teach the children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597000,"text":"I would like to say, if we want to have a sustainable world"},{"time":603000,"text":"we have to work with everything what's said,"},{"time":607000,"text":"but don't forget the cities and the children."},{"time":612000,"text":"I'm working in a museum and also a multi-use city,"},{"time":616000,"text":"because you cannot have empty places during 18 hours a day."},{"time":621000,"text":"You should have always"},{"time":624000,"text":"a structure of living and working together."},{"time":628000,"text":"Try to understand the sectors in the city"},{"time":631000,"text":"that could play different roles during the 24 hours."}]},{"cues":[{"time":637000,"text":"Another issue is, a city's like our family portrait."},{"time":641000,"text":"We don't rip our family portrait,"},{"time":644000,"text":"even if we don't like the nose of our uncle,"},{"time":649000,"text":"because this portrait is you."},{"time":652000,"text":"And these are the references that we have in any city."},{"time":658000,"text":"This is the main pedestrian mall;"},{"time":661000,"text":"we did it in 72 hours. Yes, you have to be fast."},{"time":666000,"text":"And these are the references from our ethnic contribution."},{"time":672000,"text":"This is the Italian portal,"},{"time":674000,"text":"the Ukrainian park, the Polish park, the Japanese square, the German park."},{"time":681000,"text":"All of a sudden, the Soviet Union, they split."},{"time":685000,"text":"And since we have people from"},{"time":687000,"text":"Uzbekistan, Kazakhstan, Tajikistan, [unclear],"},{"time":691000,"text":"we have to stop the program."},{"time":693000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":695000,"text":"Don't forget: creativity starts when you cut a zero from your budget."},{"time":704000,"text":"If you cut two zeros, it's much better."},{"time":709000,"text":"And this is the Wire Opera theater. We did it in two months."},{"time":716000,"text":"Parks -- old quarries that they were transformed into parks."},{"time":720000,"text":"Quarries once made the nature, and"},{"time":725000,"text":"sometimes we took this and we transformed."},{"time":729000,"text":"And every part can be transformed;"},{"time":734000,"text":"every frog can be transformed in a prince."}]},{"cues":[{"time":740000,"text":"So, in a city, you have to work fast."},{"time":744000,"text":"Planning takes time. And I'm proposing urban acupuncture."},{"time":750000,"text":"That means me, with some focal ideas to help the normal process of planning."},{"time":758000,"text":"And this is an acupuncture note --"},{"time":761000,"text":"or I.M. Pei's. Some small ones"},{"time":768000,"text":"can make the city better."},{"time":771000,"text":"The smallest park in New York, the most beautiful:"},{"time":776000,"text":"32 meters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":779000,"text":"So, I want just to end saying"},{"time":782000,"text":"that you can always propose new materials -- new sustainable materials --"},{"time":789000,"text":"but keep in mind that we have to work fast"},{"time":793000,"text":"to the end, because we don't have the whole time to plan."},{"time":803000,"text":"And I think creativity, innovation is starting."},{"time":809000,"text":"And we cannot have all the answers."},{"time":814000,"text":"So when you start --"},{"time":817000,"text":"and we cannot be so prepotent on having all the answers --"},{"time":822000,"text":"it's important starting and having the contribution from people,"},{"time":827000,"text":"and they could teach you"},{"time":830000,"text":"if you're not in the right track."}]},{"cues":[{"time":833000,"text":"At the end, I would like if you can help me to sing the sustainable song."},{"time":841000,"text":"OK?"},{"time":844000,"text":"Please, allow me just two minutes."},{"time":847000,"text":"You're going to make the music and the rhythm."}]},{"cues":[{"time":853000,"text":"♫ Toonchi-too! Toonchi-too! Toonchi-too! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":857000,"text":"♫ Toonchi-too! Toonchi-too! Toonchi-too! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":860000,"text":"♫ It's possible! It's possible! You can do it! You can do it! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":864000,"text":"♫ Use less your car! Make this decision! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":867000,"text":"♫ Avoid carbon emission! It's possible! It's possible! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":872000,"text":"♫ You can do it! You can do it! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":874000,"text":"♫ Live closer to work! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":878000,"text":"♫ Work closer to home! Save energy in your home! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":886000,"text":"♫ It's possible! It's possible! You can do it! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":889000,"text":"♫ You can do it! Separate your garbage! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":893000,"text":"♫ Organic, schmorganic! Save more! Waste less! It's possible! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":899000,"text":"♫ You can do it! Please, do it now! ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":907000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":909000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}